product.title: Unannounced Project Associate Production Engineer
product.text: Production Engineers are force multipliers who use their expertise across Bungie systems and their passion for supporting others to augment the studio's effectiveness at shipping high quality content. As a Production Engineer, you will identify improvements to our workflows and unblock and provide desk-side support to content creators often on tight deadlines. You will use this experience both to be an advocate for content creators to the Engineering org for long-term solutions and in the meantime to find workable short-term solutions to get things humming again. You will also document new knowledge and learn deeply about the various systems at play in how Bungie makes amazing games.
